{"tid":1683532,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"依家抗爭，基本上得返四個玩法","createTime":"2019-10-30T16:17:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-01T17:56:51.000Z","uid":201427,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"37e3bebe178a6988a825c151d918e28506103df9","tid":1683532,"uid":201427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T16:17:37.000Z","msg":"見到近期濫捕情況越黎越嚴重<br />\n想分享下自己既經驗<br />\n<br />\n識用任何活動<br />\n1. 唔夠人時，見防暴即走，be water, 不戀戰<br />\n2. 快速裝修，5-10分鐘內搞掂，之後轉移陣地（需有哨兵配合）<br />\n識用有大量手足時（五萬人以上）<br />\n3. 大遊行癱瘓旅遊區<br />\n4.「未解鎖」直接同黑警正面還擊，但我諗暫時人數都仲未足夠<br />\n<br />\n希望我地有一日會贏<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"634ec3e668d75554546832a9debfa41bb429fa76","tid":1683532,"uid":201427,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T16:37:45.000Z","msg":"希望大家有一日做到第4點"},{"pid":"b44902ee91108915eafb24bb5baeeb040187dec4","tid":1683532,"uid":195047,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T16:53:22.000Z","msg":"第四點好明顯係唔夠人有呢個心態<br />\n就算話要反抗都係見狗明明打得過都驚"},{"pid":"f0614bb57d0daca196fabf3036fe5559e72a8d0e","tid":1683532,"uid":201427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b44902ee91108915eafb24bb5baeeb040187dec4","tid":1683532,"uid":195047,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T16:53:22.000Z","msg":"第四點好明顯係唔夠人有呢個心態<br />\n就算話要反抗都係見狗明明打得過都驚"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T16:55:24.000Z","msg":"無計<br />\n希望有一日全民打狗會成真"},{"pid":"82b9f58ea60970b74c23815ff7bfd9906c3df6fc","tid":1683532,"uid":53612,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T16:59:35.000Z","msg":"覺得公告自己出現時間，記者影住係不智<br />\n<br />\n前線組隊轉地下"},{"pid":"a6084884aa59b2ee811815f0a7a9949bc98510fd","tid":1683532,"uid":195047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f0614bb57d0daca196fabf3036fe5559e72a8d0e","tid":1683532,"uid":201427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b44902ee91108915eafb24bb5baeeb040187dec4","tid":1683532,"uid":195047,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-